February 9, 2018 / 2:02 PM / in 2 minutes BRIEF-NGL Energy Partners Reports Qtrly Diluted Income Per Common Unit $0.32 Reuters Staff

* NGL ENERGY PARTNERS LP - ‍FISCAL 2018 ADJUSTED EBITDA TARGET IS UPDATED TO A RANGE OF $440 MILLION TO $450 MILLION​
